### ðŸ“¦ Install for Testing

1. Clone/download this repository.
2. Open Chrome and navigate to: `chrome://extensions/`
3. Enable **Developer Mode**.
4. Click **Load Unpacked** and select the `No_ad_nuke/` folder.

---

### ðŸš€ Publish to Chrome Web Store

1. Create a `.zip` of the folder (exclude `.git/`)
2. Upload to [Chrome Developer Dashboard](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/devconsole)
3. Pay one-time $5 developer fee
4. Submit for review and publish

